OL,3,CMet Office issues Amber warning for
OL,4,Csouth Wales as "heavy rain" expected
OL,6,FThe Met Office has issued an Amber
OL,7,Fwarning for rain for much of south
OL,8,FWales ahead of Monday, 1 December.
OL,10,FHeavy rain could cause flooding,
OL,11,Ftravel disruption, and the possibility
OL,12,Fof power cuts.
OL,14,FThe wet weather is expected to start
OL,15,Fovernight Sunday and into Monday with
OL,16,Fheavy rain. The warning comes into
OL,17,Fforce from the early hours of Monday
OL,18,Fmorning and will last through the day,
OL,19,Fwith heavy rain persisting until early
OL,20,Fon Tuesday, 2 December.
