OL,3,CMet Office issues Amber warning for
OL,4,Csouth Wales as "heavy rain" expected
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Met Office said:
OL,7,F"Whilst rainfall amounts will vary,
OL,8,Fthe largest accumulations are expected
OL,9,Fover the highest ground in south Wales
OL,10,Fand could reach 100-120mm through the
OL,11,Fday. 60-80mm is most likely for many
OL,12,Fhills within the Amber warning area,
OL,13,Fwhile those at lower levels should see
OL,14,Faround 20-40mm through the day."
