OL,3,CMet Office issues Amber warning for
OL,4,Csouth Wales as "heavy rain" expected
OL,6,F"Wider yellow warnings for rain have
OL,7,Falso been issued for the southwest and
OL,8,Fnorthwest of England, as well as
OL,9,Fcentral and northern parts of Wales,
OL,10,Fwith disruption also possible in these
OL,11,Fareas through the day. This is a
OL,12,Fdeveloping forecast, so it's important
OL,13,Fto stay up to date with Met Office
OL,14,Fwarnings in the coming days."
OL,16,FWithin the Amber warning area, the Met
OL,17,FOffice warned "fast flowing or deep
OL,18,Fwater is possible, which may cause a
OL,19,Fdanger to life."
