OL,3,CMet Office issues Amber warning for
OL,4,Csouth Wales as "heavy rain" expected
OL,6,FOn the risk of flooding, Richard
OL,7,FPreece, Natural Resources Wales' Duty
OL,8,FTactical Manager, said: "We are asking
OL,9,Fpeople to be alert for potential
OL,10,Fflooding with heavy rain predicted
OL,11,Fovernight on Sunday into Monday
OL,12,Fmorning, especially in parts of south
OL,13,FWales.
