OL,3,CMet Office issues Amber warning for
OL,4,Csouth Wales as "heavy rain" expected
OL,6,F"With some rivers already swollen and
OL,7,Fthe ground saturated, we expect to see
OL,8,Fa number of flood alerts and warnings
OL,9,Fissued. We also expect the rain to
OL,10,Fcause surface water issues. We're
OL,11,Furging people to be vigilant and to
OL,12,Fmake preparations for potential
OL,13,Fflooding now. You can check if you
OL,14,Flive in an area at risk of flooding on
OL,15,Four website and sign up for our free
OL,16,Fflood warning service.
OL,18,F"We also want to remind people to keep
OL,19,Faway from swollen riverbanks and not
OL,20,Fto drive or walk through flood waters
OL,21,Fas you don't know what lies beneath.
