OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F469A1764699794
OL,3,CMet Office issues Amber warning for
OL,4,Csouth Wales as "heavy rain" expected
OL,6,F"We do not provide flood warnings for
OL,7,Fflooding from surface water, so it's
OL,8,Fimportant for everyone to know their
OL,9,Fflood risk.
OL,11,F"If flooding is forecast in your area,
OL,12,Fwe want to make sure people are doing
OL,13,Fall they can to keep themselves safe.
OL,14,FThink about preparing a flood kit with
OL,15,Fany important documents and
OL,16,Fmedication, moving your car to higher
OL,17,Fground and moving treasured
OL,18,Fpossessions upstairs or to a higher
OL,19,Fplace."
